{"tid":2499819,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"執相/儲相討論","createTime":"2021-04-22T07:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T09:24:42.000Z","uid":47024,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c012b9bd0075afb02a43835c58ee9db94b0d71","tid":2499819,"uid":47024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:21:12.000Z","msg":"發覺攝台好似比較少討論影完d相點處理<br />\n等小弟拋下磚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n電腦: iMac 512GB SSD 40GB RAM<br />\n外置harddisk: G-RAID Thunderbolt 3<br />\nNAS: Qnap TS-251B<br />\n<br />\n平時影完相 第一時間係將所有相都import入Lightroom<br />\nLibrary同Cache放喺電腦SSD<br />\nFile就放喺外置harddisk 行緊4TBx2 RAID 0<br />\n<br />\n之後就即刻copy一份上NAS<br />\n行緊8TBx2 RAID 1<br />\n<br />\n執相基本上就 99%LR+1%PS<br />\n直接喺隻RAID 0上面執都算load得幾快<br />\n執完d相出JPEG 就會Up返上NAS同Google Photo<br />\n<br />\n曾經有諗過d相擺喺RAID 0好似好唔穩陣<br />\n但係起碼有隻NAS做backup<br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴打們交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"638600115bde2068190fbb20949b2c4e76f59e81","tid":2499819,"uid":113250,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:10:51.000Z","msg":"日常生活相，Raw直接掉去電腦SSD，執完JPG入NAS。有重要嘅相就External HDD，Raid 1。<br />\n<br />\n間中Delete RAW file，唔留戀，影更加多新相仲好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0419f0ee59360508469a9b84ff27ce7720db84","tid":2499819,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"全入google drive<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學生無限Storage（雖然總有一日會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"90d9b6f4d9fc93b3d12fd9b87ca3d1225192f2f1","tid":2499819,"uid":374344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"相機影Raw 過落ipad 用Lightroom執相airdrop jpeg過電話，搞掂之後將iPad啲相轉DNG過落個隻1 BT外置 SSD度。 利申：我係電腦白癡先咁做同埋屋企部notebook 太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass